20240401195416345\" tabindex=\"0\" loading=\"lazy\"><figcaption>image-20240401195416345</figcaption></figure>\n<p>也可以使用 <code v-pre>JS</code> 代码来查看。</p>\n<figure><img src=\"@source/3.系统网络/1.基本操作/assets/image-20240401195221098.png\" alt=\"image-20240401195221098\" tabindex=\"0\" loading=\"lazy\"><figcaption>image-20240401195221098</figcaption></figure>\n<p>并且往后浏览器发送请求时，还可以在运行服务端程序的服务器上看到带有 <code v-pre>cookie</code> 的请求。</p>\n<details class=\"hint-container details\"><summary>详情</summary>\n<div class=\"language-bash line-numbers-mode has-collapsed-lines collapsed\" data-highlighter=\"shiki\" data-ext=\"bash\" style=\"--vp-collapsed-lines:15;--shiki-light:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee;--shiki-light-bg:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212\"><pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark vp-code\" v-pre=\"\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\"># 服务端程序设置 cookie 后浏览器发送的请求</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\">$</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\"> ./http_server</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\"> port</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\">--</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">> </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\">标准日志:[NORMAL][pid:10844][2024-5-7</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\"> 23:10:25]</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\">\t 用户日志:socket</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">()</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\"> success</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\"> sock.hpp</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#2F798A;--shiki-dark:#4C9A91\"> 42</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#59873A;--shiki-d